Semɛun s yiman-is yenna-d : D ayen yelhan i k-d-nniɣ si tmurt n Maṣer ! Ma ɣef wedrar-agi iweɛṛen, anagar lǧerḥ-nni i d-yusan si temdint n Biri. Ma d Mmi-s n bunadem yeqqim ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi, yesɛa mmi-s n yelli-s yenna-yas : Aberdan-is : Di leɛnaya-k, m'ara d-taseḍ !
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer lɛiqab, ma d win yeṭṭfen asigna yețțțeffeɛ, a d-yas m'ara slen i wawal n Ṛebbi, acḥal ihi ț-țezdeg s wayen iwumi yezmer a d-yaweḍ ɣer webrid n leslak.
Yerna yenna-yasen : ?adret iman-nwen ɣef yiɛebbaḍ-nsen ; sṛuḥen tudert-nwen d uḍaṛṛen-nwen iwakken a ten-isellek si lehlakat-nsen ; ayen i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi s ṛṛeḥma-ines, ur yețḥellil ara deg-sen anagar ayen i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Dɣa yenna i lɣaci : ?adret iman-nwen ɣef ṭṭmeɛ imi tudert n wemdan ur d-tekki ara seg wayen yesɛa ɣas akken di rrbeḥ ameqqran i gella.
nɛedda seddaw yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin ɣef waḍu, isem-is Kluda. Mi ɣ-teɣli teflukt-nni n leslak, s leɛtab ameqqran i ț-id-nessuli ɣer lbabuṛ.
Iḍaṛṛen-nsen țɣawalen iwakken ad ssizlen abrid n Sidna Ɛisa. Iḍelben-as ad ṭṭfen seg leɛṭeṛ yeṣfan, s tezmert n Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-es.
Eɛni ixuṣṣ-ikkun leɛqel ? Amek, di tazwara tețțeklem ɣef yiman-nwen ?
Ițțubeggen-ed iman-is i sebɛa-nni n yergazen-nni n lḥebs, i geqqimen yid-es agrakal si lḥebs, armi d asmi lliɣ si lḥebs, anagar ass n westeɛfu.
Ass n westeɛfu, qṛib a nkemmel rrif n lebḥeṛ armi ț-țamdint n Ṛejyu, tnac-nni n wannaren ama di leɛmeṛ ama di tuɣzi-ines, ama di tehri-ines, ama di leɛli-ines.
M'ara ɛeddin walef iseggasen agi n usgiǧǧin ɣer tmurt n Kurnalin, si cceṛq ɣer tama n tegzirt n Kritus, ɣer tama-s tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi, si tmurt n Slusṭun, si mkul tamurt.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Mbeɛd ayagi, yiwen n lmelk yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant, yezzawer, yetɛexsi-ines n ddheb, yufa leqq-ed m'ara t-geznin ; a d-yeǧǧ aman ț-țamecṭuḥt si leqdic-is.
Mi ɛeddan ṛebɛa n teḥbulin-nni n weɣṛum d sin wudmawen, ffɣent-ed lǧețțat-nni s llebsa n leḥrir yeṣfan yețfeǧǧiǧen, beggsent-ed iman-nsent s wagusen n tmes.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Mi gțeddu ad yerkeb di lbabuṛ ɣer tmurt n Surya, yesla belli at Isṛail mcawaṛen iwakken a t-xedɛen ; dɣa ibeddel ṛṛay, iṭṭef abrid ad yuɣal d amezwaru.
ur qbilen ara ad ṭṭfen di tiṭ-is, qṛib a ten-yeǧǧ ad yali wayen yelhan si tmurt n Asya. M'ara qqaṛen : Lesṛuḥ-nni ilaq ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Tameṭṭut-nni tenna-yas : A k-d-sbeddeɣ-k aț-țesɛeddiḍ snat n wagguren iṣurdiyen i kra n yergazen n yergazen, s wakka aț-țḥemdeḍ Ṛebbi di leqdic n wussan.
