Akken qṛib ad yeɣli yiṭij, ataya Sidi Ṛebbi iteddu-d ɣef wuḍar s ufella n waman, agur yuɣal d abrid ur nesɛi azal. Mi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer dinna, s wakka a nqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-sen, lqebṭan n tejmaɛt akk-d Izimer.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen.
