S wakka, s yiwen n wass i deg ara d-yesseɣlay di lqaɛa. Akken daɣen i tedṛa d Cciṭan i gzemren a t-iɛaqeb Sidi Ṛebbi Bab n tezmert tameqqrant di liman, i tella yiwet n tikkelt i deg ara t-iɛiwnen seg uwrent, iwakken a tent-id-yaweḍ ɣer yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus.
Sidna Ɛisa yenna-yas : Tumam ! Axaṭer lemmer ț-țideț, tili imezdaɣ n temdint n ?udum, tili imezdaɣ-ines a ten-id-yaweḍ ugeffur, tili imezdaɣ-ines a d-yuɣal uqbel ad yali.
Sidi Ṛebbi yekkes tazmert i lḥekmat ț-țzemmar n igenwan, ikcef itent-id zdat txelqit meṛṛa, iɣleb-itent s lmut n Mmi-s ɣef wumidag.
Leɛqiṛa tețwaṭṭef nețțat d nnbi nni n lekdeb i gxeddmen lbeṛhanat seddaw n lḥekma-s, s wayes ikellex imdanen meṛṛa yețwaḍebɛen s ṭṭabeɛ n lekdeb. M'ara tekcem-iten tugdi, imiren setɛeṛfen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi Bab n igenwan, ḥemden-t.
Tenɛețțab aṭas ger ifassen n ṭṭeba, nețțawi-d.
