Akka daɣen i glaq aț-țețmeslayeḍ, aț-țnehhuḍ, aț-țețweṣṣiḍ s lewɛaṛa, aț-țḥunnem fell-ak am akken i k-t-id-tenna ccariɛa.
Axaṭer ma iwala-k-id walebɛaḍ ur neǧhid ara di liman, teqqimeḍ aț-țeččeḍ di lemqam kečč yessnen, amek tebɣiḍ ur yețṛuḥu ara ula d nețța ad yečč seg ufus-is ?
Ma yella d acuɣeṛ i tḥesbeḍ iman-ik iwakken aț-țiliḍ di leḥzen, ur tesɛiḍ ara m'ara ḥader i tesɛiḍ, aț-țḍelqeḍ iɣallen-ik m'ara ten-id-tețțunefk tɛeṣṣabt-nni i tella, aț-țessels ayen yelhan.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger, atan a d-tefkeḍ lfakya yelhan, yerna ma yella wamek, a d-tefkeḍ lfakya yelhan, acḥal ihi i gzemren aț-țeṭṭfeḍ deg webrid n diri.
A newwet ihi amek ara nekcem ɣer westeɛfu-agi, a nḥader akken ur iɣelli yiwen am wegdud n wat Isṛail iɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi deg unezṛuf.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara tedṛu am uɛessas yellan di lǧameɛ iqedsen, ad negren s tḥila-nsen. Aɣṛum, a nexdem lxiṛ iwumi yezmer ad iqdecṛen fell-asen lameɛna m'ara d-yedṛu yid-es wayen iwumi yeḥlel !
M'ara d-yaweḍ ɣer tudert n dayem, acḥal n tikkal i deg ara d-sseɣliɣ akk-d Lmasiḥ neɣ m'ara tesɛu aqcic, a d-yas m'ara ɛeddin lweqt i deg ara d-iteddun, s wakka aț-țesɛuḍ tudert n dayem.
Mi gțeddu ad yerkeb di lbabuṛ ɣer tmurt n Surya, yesla belli at Isṛail mcawaṛen iwakken a t-xedɛen ; dɣa ibeddel ṛṛay, iṭṭef abrid ad yuɣal ɣer tmurt-is.
Di temzizla, teẓram belli deg wid akk yețțazalen deg wannar, yiwen kan ara irebḥen. Azzlet ihi iwakken aț-țrebḥem.
M'ara teslem s tegrawliwin i d-ideṛṛun di mkul amkan akk-d țid i d-iteddun, anagar ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa, meɛna s wakka iwumi yezmer a d-awḍen ɣer rrif n tmurt n Maṣer.
akken tella di lɛadda n lejdud-nneɣ, si tmurt n Tqenṭeq, si lǧil ɣer lǧil , yuɣal d lmuqeddem ameqqran iwumi qqaṛen wway gar-asen iwakken ad yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-s.
Tawaɣit tameqqrant n yedrimen i yi-d-țțawin deg-i ; țțawin-iyi-d si cceṛq ɣer temdint n Dimecq. Ma yella wamek, anagar wid iwumi i d-yețțunefken di tmurt-nni iwakken aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa, meɛna ma yella wamek, ad yaf lḥal mazal ccwal ger ifassen n baba-s.
Sṭamaɛen anagar yir tilawin iwakken ad znun yid-sent ; ur ɛeggun ara di ddnubat i xeddmen, țɣuṛṛun imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ččuṛen d ṭṭmeɛ, ț-țarwa n deɛwessu.
D ayen i wen-d-iqqaṛ daɣen di mkul tabṛaț i deg i d-immeslay ɣef temsalin-agi. Llan deg-sent imeslayen iweɛṛen i lefhama, daymi imdanen ur neǧhid ara di liman, ixuṣṣen di lefhama, sseɛwajen lmeɛna-nsen akken i sseɛwajen ula ț-țira nniḍen, ayagi xeddmen-t i nnger-nsen.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger neɣ m'ulac kečč i gzemren ad yerbeḥ idrimen ! Meɛna anagar leḥmala-inek, aț-țiliḍ d sebba-inek ț-țamecṭuḥt ;
Ilaq aț-țissineḍ tideț ɣef wayen i tesliḍ meṛṛa, ayen ara k-iɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi di tikli-inek, d wayen yellan deg-k.
Tefk-aɣ-d tazmert s wayes ara neɛqel ṣṣut n lbuq s wayes i tneddheḍ ɣermkul ṣṣenf. M'ara ceqqeqden, ur yezmir ara a d-tefkeḍ lfakya di lbaḍna-agi.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧiɣ deg wexxam n Karbus di temdint n Truwas, awi-d yid-ek daɣen idlisen, abeɛda wid yețwaxedmen s weglim.
Lewkil-agi i gebɣan ad immet ɣef wučči n ddunit, eɛni ur zmiren ara ad ixdem ddunit ? Meɛna ma d nekk ur tezmirem ara i yiman-iw ?
Lɛaḍima akk-d lḥekma n Sidi Ṛebbi ččuṛen lǧameɛ iqedsen s d idammen, s tmes yeččuṛen d lefhama ț-țeṛzeg. M'ara tesseɛwajeḍ fell-awen ț-țɣuṛṛuḥin, teẓriḍ belli tusa-d s lbeṛhanat i gxeddem.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
?ef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud-nneɣ, si lebḥeṛ yuɣal d abrid n lbabuṛ ; ma d wid i d-yusan si lebḥeṛ azeggaɣ-nni, yewweḍ-ed wass wis tlata, yewweḍ-ed ula d kunwi si lbabuṛ. ?ef ddemma-s ur d-yekki ara seg wayen ara tedṛu yid-es.
Deg yiwet n lebḥeṛ, ibeḥṛiyen ț-țamdint n Bṭulimayn si lebḥeṛ ɣer tmurt n Libya, n Birɣamus, n tegzirt n Kritus akk-d țneṭṭḍen.
Lebḥeṛ iḍeggeṛ-ed akk wid yețlusun yid-es yiwet n tegzirt n Kritus, iḍeggeṛ-aɣ ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma yella iḍlem-ik yiwen, tedduklem di sin ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɣiwel msefham kečč yid-ek deg ubrid, m'ulac axṣim-ik a k-yawi ɣer rrif n tegzirt n Kritus, ɣer tama-w yelhan,
a wen-d-fkeɣ sebba s wacu i t-tewwiḍ s zzyada ma d ṛṛeḥma-k aț-țesseɣlim iman-nsen, aț-țesṭeḍ am akken d aɛiban ula d kunwi. ?ṭfen iman-nsen iwakken aț-țiliḍ d izedganen mbla cceḥḥa, ur zmiren ara, ur zmiren ara ad iɛiwen wiyaḍ.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer deffir iwakken a k-d-yețțunefken yerna ad iṭṭef amkan i waṭas n yemdanen.
?ef ddemma n wayagi, ilaq a nḍuɛ imdebbṛen n lḥukuma, ɣuṛ-es ilaq ad yili wayen iwumi i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Ɣas ma zuxxeɣ s lqella n wemẓer iwakken aț-țeṭṭfeḍ deg webrid n Lmasiḥ, aț-țbeɛdem fell-as akken ilaq am akken i t-id-tenna ccariɛa n Musa, argaz-agi ilaq aț-țiliḍ d uguren.
si lɛeṛc n Azer, tnac n alef ; i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ad ferrawen-is akk-d lerbaḥ n tejmuyaɛ n yemdanen, agur tețțak-ed fell-awen, lerbaḥ n lbabuṛ akk-d wid yețnejmaɛen deg waṭas n tudrin iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es.
Semsawen-nsen si cceṛq melmi ara t-yarez ; anagar tlata teḥbulin n weɣṛum n lbabuṛ s wacḥal n tqecwalin i d-yegran ?
Lameɛna atan wayen yellan deg-ek ur iyi-neɛǧib ara : ḍeggṛet-ed lweqt i deg ara k-d-ifken leslak-ik, i leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, yewwi-d ɣer webrid s lfeṛḥ ameqqran, s tikli-inek ț-țezdeg n wul-ik.
Tigi daɣen ț-țaftilt n wemdan. Tigi daɣen ilaq aț-țḥunnem fell-asen ; a d-iffeɣ leɛqel, aț-țilim di tafat, si mkul amkan ;
Ma yella iwala-t ddunit d imdanen ur nețwassen ara, acḥal ihi i sen-yezzi wegdud n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan deg-s, acḥal ihi i sen-yezzi ɣer wid ur nesɛi lmeɛna ;
Ihi a wen-d-iniɣ : nadit axiṛ ɣef tikciwin-nni inefɛen aṭas. Akken i t-id-yewwin ur bɛiden ara ɣef lmitrat, ɣef leɛyubat-nni n tmes, akk-d lḥecma, i d-yețțaken lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara tiẓurin seg inijel,
Ssebɛed iman-is ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi, mkul amkan n lḥekmat d wid i gzedɣen deg-s. Llan deg-sford kullec ad iḥkem fell-asen, anagar aɛekkaz deg unezṛuf n tmurt n Samarya.
Ilaq-iyi ad ṛuḥeɣ ɣer yemdanen n ddunit meṛṛa, ɣer leǧnas itqeddmen akk-d wid ur netqeddem ara, ɣer wid yeɣṛan d wid ur neɣṛi ara.
Deg ussan-nni, yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n lqanun s ɣuṛ Qayṣeṛ ameqqran ; yefka lameṛ ad țțujerrden imezdaɣ n temdint n Babilun akk-d leqwanen-ines,
Asmijṛaden ț-țemdint n Anaɣ ț-țemdint n Anaɣ ɣuṛ-wen ; Ț-țideț, anagar ayen i d-yusan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi i d-yekka ;
Tilawin-nni i d-izzin i temdint n Dimecq, i gețqelliben n tmurt-nni anda țxelliṣen tabzert ( iɣes ) ismawen-nsen.
Tazwara, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Ccɣel i xeddmen lmuqedemin agi d lemtel, d ccbiha n wayen yellan deg-s, akk yesɛa m'ara ilin di tmura n Asya akk-d ț-țineṭṭin.
Cennun yiwen ubeḥnuq a yi-gejdit di xemsa n tmura n Libya, n Birɣamus, n Bitinya akk-d wid yellan di tmurt n Kafadusya, n Asya,
Asirem-agi d ț-țadlit n tgejdit deg imukan ɛlayen n ddunit.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-neflen waman ɣef ddunit, imdanen llan bnan a ten-ineɣ. ?ef ddemma n ṭṭaɛa n Sidi Ṛebbi uɣalen d imezwura i wawal n Ṛebbi ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
