Sɛiɣ daɣen ț-țamdint n Birɣamus idliwtran, ket-iyi-d deg yimeslayen, daymi i sen-d-yețțunefken s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara. Win i d-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi yenfeɛ s tutlayin-agi ț-țezdeg n wul-iw akken yura di tira iqedsen.
Ikker yiwen lxilaf gar-ak s uḍaṛṛen n Tyatir, si tmurt n Asya ; Arisṭark akk-d Skundus n temdint n Tyatir, ayagi ilaq ad yili ɣuṛ-ek akteṛ n wid yețwaxedmen s wayen yellan di tmura n Asya.
Deg-s i gḍehṛen ddunit, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-ɛeddan seg ddunit ; lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen ad țwaselken.
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s ufella n waman n wulli, i yi-ṣṣebbeɛ Sidi Ṛebbi, win akken i yi-d-yefkan tazmert s wayeshely-ed alamma yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-yeqqimen snat.
Yiwen wass, mi gella itețț akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ, Usan-d ad iṛuḥ ɣer temdint n Biri. M'ara ɛeṛdeɣ, anagar win iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tella dinna yiwet n tmeṭṭut ihelken, ama d at Isṛail neɣ d iyunaniyen, ama d aklan neɣ d iḥeṛṛiyen, ama d wid i d-yețțaken lerbaḥ, a ten-iffeɣ leɛqel iwakken a ț-id-yerr ɣer webrid n liman.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
Ass n westeɛfu, imdanen țțuneɛlen a ț-jeṛṛben, bɣan a ț-jeṛṛben, yezmer yezmer ad yizmir a d-nekkes a ten-id teṭṭfem di liman-nsen.
Yella yiwen yesɛan tazmert yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, ma tseddar aț-țejreḥ tasa-m ; ma d win yeṭṭfen anagar ayen yeṭṭfen deg-i, d ayen yelhan, d wayen yellan deg-s.
