Imdanen n ddunit meṛṛa ad ilin di lfeṛḥ ameqqran imi mmuten. Ad țemceggaɛen tirezfin wway gar-asen,awen-d am akken tɣawsiwin-nni i ț-teččuṛen n tmes, او akk-d ukubri.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen. LLlan daɣen wid iḥeṛmen iman-nsen ɣef zwaǧ, ɣef tmura n Asya.
A nelḥu ɛinani s tezdeg akk-d ṣṣfa, di tafat n wass ; xḍut i ssikṛan d ccehwat, i leɛdez d lexdayem icemten, i čaqlalat ț-țismin.
Di yal lḥaǧa, ilaq aț-țeṭṭfem deg webrid n Lmasiḥ, win akken i geddan yid-es yiwen seg ubeḥri m'ara nili yid-es.
